advisories.title: ELSA-2024-3304:  libreoffice security fix update (IMPORTANT)
advisories.description:
[1:5.3.6.1-26.0.1]
- adjust color palette to match Redwood style.
- Replaced RedHat colors with Oracle colors, and the filename redhat.soc with oracle.soc in specfile
- Build with --with-vendor='Oracle America, Inc.'

[1:5.3.6.1-26]
- Fix CVE-2022-38745 Empty entry in Java class path
- Fix CVE-2023-0950 Array Index UnderFlow in Calc Formula Parsing
- Fix CVE-2023-1183 libreoffice: Arbitrary File Write
- Fix CVE-2023-6185 escape url passed to gstreamer
